    Get a specific domain from a SDTM object

    domain.Rd

    Get a specific domain from a SDTM object

    Usage

    domain(obj, name)

    Arguments

    obj

    The sdtm object.

    name

    The domain to return.

    Value

    The specified domain as data.frame

    Examples

    domain(examplinib, "dm")
